BLOCKERS FIXED (Codex CNS-019):

#1: check_policy now evaluates real policy semantics:
    - Autonomy policies: intent authorization + mode enforcement
    - Tool calling policies: allowed/blocked tools + enabled check
    - Provider guardrails: provider enabled + model allowlist
    - Generic: required_fields, blocked_values, limits (existing)

#2: MCP ToolGateway loads policy_tool_calling.v1.json (not hardcoded)
    - MCP governance tools always enabled (they ARE governance)
    - max_rounds from policy artifact

#3: Provider guardrails enforced in build_request():
    - Only workspace override policy (bundled defaults are reference-only)
    - PROVIDER_DISABLED → ValueError (fail-closed)

#4: build_request_with_context loads canonical + workspace_facts:
    - Canonical decisions from canonical_store.query()
    - Workspace facts from .cache/index/workspace_facts.v1.json
    - Facts format normalized (list → dict)

#5: end_session auto-promotes high-confidence decisions:
    - promote_from_ephemeral(min_confidence=0.7) on session close

367 tests passing, all lint clean.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
